<h1>John Clarks Invoice for Services, with Jeffersons Approval</h1>

<div class="docbody">
<table class="bodytext">
<tr>
	      <td style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0;">The Commonwealth To John Clark Dr</td>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;"></td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>1780 April</td>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;"></td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td><span class="space" title="space in original source" style="padding-left:1.5em; padding-right:1.5em;"></span>To a large table for the Council Chamber</td>
