	      <td style="text-align: right; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">050</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td><span class="space" title="space in original source" style="padding-left:1.5em; padding-right:1.5em;"></span>To Mending a table for the Clerks Pr. Do.</td>
	      <td style="text-align: right; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">0100</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td><span class="space" title="space in original source" style="padding-left:1.5em; padding-right:1.5em;"></span>To 2 Days work at the Pallice Council Chamber &amp;c</td>
	      <td style="text-align: right; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">100</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td><span class="space" title="space in original source" style="padding-left:1.5em; padding-right:1.5em;"></span>To 100 Brads for Do.</td>
