</table>
<table class="bodytext">
<tr>
	      <td colspan="4">At the preisent price of provisions 350.<a class="ptr" href="#TSJN-01-04-0282-fn-0001" id="TSJN-01-04-0282-fn-0001-ptr">1</a></td>
